preference.name: COMMONcatiatojt_CATPart_ets_nr_types
preference.preference_description: Specifies the CATIA v5 CATPart dataset named references necessary for translation. All named reference types specified by this preference must exist for a dataset of this type to be translated. If no named reference types are specified, no named reference type validation is performed. Valid Values: Accepts multiple strings as values. Each string must be an existing named reference type.
